<item>
            <title>[HBASE-16684] The get() requests does not see locally buffered put() requests when autoflush is disabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-16684</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When autoflush is disabled the put() requests are buffered locally.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Subsequent get() requests on the same host will always go to the network and will not see the updates that are buffered locally.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13006901">HBASE-16684</key>
